data.description: So much potential!  Fenced 7.1 acres with 7 outbuildings. Detached 1000 sq ft garage w/220, heated with stove. Also a second garage or storage unit. Best feature just might be the 5 stall two story barn so bring your horses! The manufactured home has been rented and now vacant. Needs updating in kitchen, baths & flooring. Deck in rear can be slippery. Hot tub and refrigerator are of no value. Seller to do no work orders. Cash out.This property has 4 parcel numbers.
